Context: George Brown College provides a public Wi-Fi network (GBC-Public) for visitors, offering basic internet access for email and browsing but not supporting high-bandwidth activities like streaming. This network does not grant access to internal college resources for students and employees. The personal information used to log in is kept private and will never be sold or provided to third parties. For application deadlines, college news, upcoming events, tours, and more, visitors can sign up on the website. Contact information includes phone number 416-415-2000, TTY: 1-877-515-5559, email ask.george@georgebrown.ca, and social media hub. The information contained in this website is subject to change without notice.
